data.message: hi facebook. i just want to report some problem. i can't upload videos that i want to upload. it always says that "some parts of this video belongs to someone". please help me.

replies.message: Hi Vince. Your ability to upload videos has been disabled because you have repeatedly uploaded videos which appear to contain copyrighted material owned by a third party. If you think that we've removed these videos by mistake, you can file a counter notice for each video by following the links provided in the warning emails you received. -Meagan
